1852
01:21:31,652 --> 01:21:32,853
<i>I'm here for you.</i>

1853
01:21:32,887 --> 01:21:34,631
<i>And I want you to know
I'm gonna take care of you,</i>

1854
01:21:34,655 --> 01:21:35,657
<i>I promise that.</i>

1855
01:21:36,157 --> 01:21:37,191
<i>Okay?</i>

1856
01:21:37,224 --> 01:21:38,626
