1911
01:24:37,872 --> 01:24:41,209
but what you do with the truth
once you have it.

1912
01:24:48,649 --> 01:24:51,619
I think you have something
you wanna tell me.

1913
01:24:53,420 --> 01:24:56,290
I think you're very perceptive

1914
01:24:56,323 --> 01:24:59,527
