1917
01:25:12,473 --> 01:25:13,808
I'm in no rush.

1918
01:25:15,309 --> 01:25:16,410
In fact,

1919
01:25:16,443 --> 01:25:18,513
I find it quiet pleasant

1920
01:25:18,546 --> 01:25:20,215
