Lawyers were here.

1922
01:25:29,623 --> 01:25:31,192
Very big lawyers,
it looked like.

1923
01:25:31,225 --> 01:25:33,327
They left all this stuff
and business cards.

1924
01:25:33,360 --> 01:25:34,704
And there was
a pile of other stuff

1925
