1969
01:27:35,516 --> 01:27:36,784
Yeah.

1970
01:27:36,817 --> 01:27:38,919
Yeah, with the right
lawyers, you know?

1971
01:27:38,952 --> 01:27:40,388
Not these local guys,

1972
